title: World of Gnawa: Traditional Moroccan Music (2001, M4A)
description:
World of Gnawa (2001, Rounder Records)

This is a 2-CD collection of traditional Gnawa music from Morocco. It has some really interesting polyrhythms and instrumentation, and is a cool little glance at a completely new world of music.

The album is featured in the book 1000 Recordings to Hear Before You Die.
